features.text:
Dr. Qiaoming Mi  米巧铭博士

graduated from the Repin Academy of Fine Arts in Russia, researcher of China Academy of Art, member of American Portrait Painting Association. Many works have been collected by Clinton and many other dignitaries and celebrities. From 2018 to 2020, he won the "Hurun Art List" for three consecutive years. In the public auction market in 2019, the work "Dream Buddha" was sold for 12.282 million yuan.
毕业于俄罗斯列宾美术学院。中国美术家协会会员，中国美术学院研究员，美国肖像画协会会员。多个作品被克林顿等许多政要和名人收藏。 2018年至2020年连续​​三年荣获“胡润艺术榜”。 2019年公开拍卖市场，作品《梦佛》以1228.2万元成交。

Work: Dream Buddha

Author: Mi Qiaoming

Auction price: 12.282 million yuan

2019 Beijing Hanhai Spring Auction



作品：梦佛

作者：米巧铭

成交价：1228.2万元

2019年北京瀚海春季拍卖会

Professor Rude Yu 余润德教授

Famous contemporary artist. Vice Chairman of the Chinese Society of Art Association, Executive Dean of the Central University of Finance and Economics, Double-appointed Professor of Renmin University of China, Researcher of the Central Academy of Fine Arts, Distinguished Professor of Communication University of China, Distinguished Professor of Xiamen University, Asian Art Advisor of the American Rodin International Artist Foundation. His works have participated in internationally influential exhibitions and held solo exhibitions in important domestic academic institutions and art galleries. Representative works: "The Temptation of Alienation", "Invisible Flame", "Fuzzy Light", "Impression of Peach Blossom", "The Edge of Weightlessness", "Unusual Freedom" and other series.

当代著名艺术家。 中国社会艺术协会副主席，中央财经大学画院执行院长，中国人民大学双聘教授，中央美术学院研究员，中国传媒大学特聘教授，厦门大学特聘教授，美国罗丹国际艺术家基金会亚洲区艺术顾问。作品多次参加国际有影响力的展览，并在国内重要学术机构和美术馆举办个展。 代表作：《疏离的诱惑》《隐身之焰》《模糊的光芒》《印象桃花》《失重的边缘》《异样的自由》等系列。

田峰源

独⽴艺术家，nft艺术家，设计师，插画师。现居深圳。
2009年考⼊中央美术学院附中。
2014年就读于意⼤利Brera美术学院，获纯艺术学⼠学位，视觉艺术硕⼠学位。

#作品阐述:

The dream of the brain is more 
often a multi-dimensional space
, in which any realistic image will be covered by multi-dimensional consciousness, forming those figures, numbers, colors, etc., which are difficult for us to understand in the dream. This is similar to how computer data is presented. Is the chaotic representation of dreams a dimension beyond human understanding in reality? The work is created in the form of NFT (virtual non-homogenous token) and is displayed in the three-digit space. On the one hand, it shows the same form of digitization and "dream", on the other hand, it shows this kind of entanglement.
Time is a one-way line can not turn back. Dreams may be a higher dimensional world. Here everything can be reversed, time can be turned back, and narrative possibilities are endless.
大脑的梦境更多时候是一个多维的空间，
在其中的任何现实中的图像都会被多维意识
覆盖，形成梦境中我们难以理解的那些图形、
数字、颜色等。这和电脑数据呈现方式类似。
梦境的混沌呈现是否是高于现实中人类理解
的维度。作品以NFT（虚拟非同质代币）的形式创作，
并在三位空间进行展示。一方面展示
了数字化与“梦境”化的形式相同，另一方面将这种纠缠展示。
时间是单向线⽆法回头。梦境也许是⼀种更⾼维度的空间世界。
在这⾥⼀切可以颠倒，时间可以倒退，叙事
拥有⽆数可能性。
